<!-- UPDATE: Set title for Acceptable Use Policy -->
  <b>
  Welcome to the the Tufts University Network
  </b>
  <p/>
  In order to access the Tufts University Network you must agree to comply with Tufts' Information Stewardship Policy and supporting Use and Information Policies (see below.)
  <p/>
  After clicking "I Accept", you may access the network. These are your connection options:
  <p/>

<ul>
  <li>
    <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><b>Tufts Secure Wireless</b></span> (recommended for all wireless devices)<br>
    SSID:  tufts-secure
    <p/>

    <ul>
      <li>
        Login using your Tufts username and password - <b>No additional Device Registration required</b>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <p/>

  <li>
    <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><b>Tufts Wireless</b></span> (general wireless network)<br>
    SSID:  tuftswireless
    <p/>
  
    <ul>
      <li>
        Login using your Tufts username and password, after which you will be presented with the Device Registration page. - <b>Requires separate Device Registration</b>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <p/>

  <li>
    <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><b>Tufts Wired</b></span> (recommended for desktop & devices  that do not use wireless connections)
    <p/>

    <ul>
      <li>
      Login using your Tufts username and password, after which you will be presented with the Device Registration page. - <b>Requires separate Device Registration</b>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <p/>

  <li>
    <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><b>Tufts Guest Wireless</b></span> (Open Guest wireless network)<br>
    SSID:  tufts-guest
    <p/>

    <ul>
      <li>
        <b>No Login or Device Registration required</b>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>


  <p/>
  If your device does not correctly display the Information Stewardship
  Policy and supporting Use and Information Policies, you may
  <a href=/portal_resources/html/rispover.html>click here</a> to view these documents
  in a simpler format
